2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper focuses on providing security guarantees for wireless communication, which is a key area of research in cryptography and security. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with wireless communication, which is a key area of research in networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with wireless optical communication, which is a type of multimedia communication. 
5. cs.OH (Other Computer Science) - The paper may also be classified under this category as it deals with a specialized area of computer science that may not fit neatly into any of the other categories.
